channel.title: mycatalog updates
channel.description: 'My Catalog' uses the IBM Cloud catalog API to retrieve data from the catalog. It attempts to be as accurate as possible. This feed shows additions, updates, removals from the catalog. Use with care. It is a work-in-progress :)

item.title: [updated] Match 360 (mdm-oc) has changed the description of the plan named lite
item.description: *before*: This plan provides you with a free 30-day trial of IBM Match 360, a multi-domain operational and analytical master data management (MDM) service that delivers at scale an integrated and consolidated view of critical enterprise data across data silos, leveraging intelligent and tunable data matching and entity resolution as well as management of other related entities across the enterprise. Trial plan services are deleted after 30 days, *after*: This plan provides you with a free 30-day trial of IBM Master Data Management, a multi-domain operational and analytical master data management (MDM) service that delivers at scale an integrated and consolidated view of critical enterprise data across data silos, leveraging intelligent and tunable data matching and entity resolution as well as management of other related entities across the enterprise. Trial plan services are deleted after 30 days
